{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d2f10a904b","title":"毛泽东转发华东军区党委关于打虎预算报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4be3e1df7b","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":30,"articleId":"d2f10a904b"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3e425491bb","type":"title","text":"毛泽东转发华东军区党委关于打虎预算报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d2f10a904b"},{"id":"91224448fb","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d2f10a904b"},{"id":"d9553eb317","type":"appellation","text":"各大军区，志愿军，并各中央局：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d2f10a904b"},{"id":"2a21253c6b","type":"paragraph","text":"华东军区一月二十九日规定打虎预算的精神很好，发给你们参考。一个大军区不会只有两百多个大老虎，但第一次规定这样一个数目是适当的，以后可以根据认识的深入逐步追加打虎任务。中央一级十二万人，清出贪污分子一万人（百分之八十以上是一百万元以下的小贪污分子，一般须从轻处理），已经清出或准备清出的大老虎四百只，这是经过多次严加督促、不断追加任务才达成的奋斗目标。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d2f10a904b"},{"id":"546ec9b82f","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一月三十日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d2f10a904b"}],"page":{"id":"64c6298496","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"d2f10a904b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}